casebody.data:
Teresa BUCHANAN, Petitioner,
v.
F. King ALEXANDER, et al. No. 19-274. Supreme Court of the United States. Oct. 21, 2019.

Motion of National Coalition Against Censorship, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.
